summary: Music compilation of varied songs to be used with the Personalized Music Mod.
descriptionHtml: This is a music compilation of varied songs, poems and theme music from sources such as : The Witcher 3, Dragon Age, Legend of Zelda, Diablo 1&2, Lord of the Rings, Harry Potter, Malukah, Adrian von Ziegler, Trailer Music and many more. This is to be used in conjunction with No_Aardvarks_Allowed's awesome Personalized Music - Add your own music to Skyrim mod. I extended and pieced together many from scratch with Audacity and converted them. Enjoy! Credit to No_Aardvarks_Allowed for the original mod of Personalized Music - Add your own music to Skyrim for without him and his effort this wouldn't be possible, thank you! Also many many thanks to the fine artist and directors of the Movies, Games and Music that is contained within. Install : extract Data to temp location, navigate to your Skyrim Data folder and drop into your music folders added by Personalized Music for Skyrim. Example : MMCastle01 goes to the Castle folder. Rinse lather and repeat.
author: Sagegem
